movies.title: 44 Minutes: The North Hollywood Shoot-Out
movies.plot: After a failed bank robbery, two heavily armed men hold the Los Angeles Police Department at bay for 44 minutes.
movies.awards: Nominated for 2 Primetime Emmys. Another 2 nominations.
